{"tid":1780833,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌老母，蝗蟲真係要滅絕","createTime":"2019-12-12T16:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T00:55:02.000Z","uid":116465,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa623f6664c9e7ccf724b3c8c862dd65a2d6cd0","tid":1780833,"uid":116465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先去完周同學公祭，<br />\n落返大圍有d口渴，<br />\n咪順便去7仔用埋果一蚊囉。<br />\n呀屌，果間舖細細間，<br />\n一入去有隻老蝗女痴撚左線係咁問我攞電話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我黑人問號左，<br />\n加上心情唔多靚咪拿拿林拎支茶俾錢走囉。<br />\n揀茶果陣先知道隻蝗買左張電話卡要即場試，<br />\n同埋佢又唔多識用，咪周圍煩鳩人囉。<br />\n最後佢勁大吵大鬧煩個店員，<br />\n店員頂唔撚順俾左自己個電話號碼佢試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我心諗做乜鳩，都係走啦。<br />\n你老母，今次到佢個唔知蝗孫定蝗仔，<br />\n睇落似得兩三歲。<br />\n無啦啦攔撚住我(似係想搵人玩)，<br />\n即刻無名火起一手撥開佢叫佢行撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n稚兒無罪？<br />\n有咁既長輩第時會教出咩人真係可想而知。<br />\n<br />\n今次運動既其中一個目的，<br />\n就係大家都唔想同蝗同化，恥與為伍。<br />\n佢地黑全世界憎，唔係無道理。<br />\n財大氣粗，無文化，無禮貌。<br />\n自私自利，自卑又自大，<br />\n無愛心無人性無道德無廉恥。<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢個民族幾時先會滅亡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5126bd7d63e0175fd311e8399159051134babc3","tid":1780833,"uid":38793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲的侵佔 腐蝕這都市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d293b394798581e7d611a67b9724ca40bc221b4","tid":1780833,"uid":269202,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:33:29.000Z","msg":"香港都有呢d客，係本地人<br />\n你指既呢類客係屬於婦孺，係會不安同埋多要求，因為唔識，以為電話卡試左唔得有得換<br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁小事都扣民族帽子好危險，同習思想一樣<br />\n我覺得你唔好，危害到國家就種族滅絕...<br />\n希特拉？昂山素姬？新疆？"},{"pid":"15c9dd14d35c6a8f611c383470bdc8c4ef353da1","tid":1780833,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發動世界級遊行！Who stand with us世界巡遊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ae73862dac45b49a23632ebb20d4624e8ac5b30","tid":1780833,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"針對人格，而非針對種族。唔好比血統、出生地之類既先天因素，唔係令香港人互相分化同歧視既理由。"},{"pid":"e65a6c3376ea1827ec9b6c88a661db27faf44fe3","tid":1780833,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>針對人格，而非針對種族。血統、出生地之類既先天因素，唔係令香港人互相分化同歧視既理由。</blockquote><br />\n更正"},{"pid":"7b8992a476d3aa04d302b7d656d2396bb33d2c1b","tid":1780833,"uid":211362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:26:38.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81498b35fba62601aec2eb9ec5f4785ad342016e","tid":1780833,"uid":116465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d293b394798581e7d611a67b9724ca40bc221b4","tid":1780833,"uid":269202,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:33:29.000Z","msg":"香港都有呢d客，係本地人<br />\n你指既呢類客係屬於婦孺，係會不安同埋多要求，因為唔識，以為電話卡試左唔得有得換<br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁小事都扣民族帽子好危險，同習思想一樣<br />\n我覺得你唔好，危害到國家就種族滅絕...<br />\n希特拉？昂山素姬？新疆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T23:26:19.000Z","msg":"鍵盤下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又無核彈又唔係奇拿。<br />\n<br />\n當然明，<br />\n就算去到世界認為普遍質素高既日本人，<br />\n都有大把痴線佬。<br />\n無差別殺人，<br />\n童黨姦殺無辜少女等滅絕人性既case都聽過。<br />\n<br />\n我同意你講呢類人係婦孺，<br />\n唔止香港，全球都會有。<br />\n但你唔覺得咩？<br />\n呢個種族既人，係特別有<span style=\"color: red;\">侵犯性</span><br />\n無論佢地識野唔識野好，<br />\n同呢個世界既普世價值，<br />\n點都係唔多接軌。<br />\n<br />\n原因當然知道係政府出事，<br />\n無教育好人民仲四圍放d人出去攪事。<br />\n前排曱曱仲話係日本人跟唔到佢地既文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連最高領導人都係咁講野，<br />\n呢個民族仲點有得救？"},{"pid":"f061147a1747914fc33bf2273ad856baa0562995","tid":1780833,"uid":116465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e65a6c3376ea1827ec9b6c88a661db27faf44fe3","tid":1780833,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>針對人格，而非針對種族。血統、出生地之類既先天因素，唔係令香港人互相分化同歧視既理由。</blockquote><br />\n更正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"無錯。<br />\n<br />\n絕對認同應該要每一個case獨立審視。<br />\n<br />\n只不過想講，純粹數據上，<br />\n中國人惹人厭既機率真係普遍多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f063d92295f4834d1525fe3e83ed07a11295fb31","tid":1780833,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T23:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UybFcm7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUybFcm7.gif&h=40c544d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omgRi18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomgRi18.jpg&h=f8a067a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSBt5G9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSBt5G9.jpg&h=85e3f077&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6f0ff9a26b2ee739e912d58ef1e5a10eaf6d0a9","tid":1780833,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T23:47:01.000Z","msg":"又要多謝民主黨李柱銘等人為莊豐源打官司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgm